text: Aizhan Akilbayeva (born 13 September 1991) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Aizhan Akilbayeva, Getty * Aizhan Akilbayeva, Zimbio Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
